    <link href="//www.marks-jewelers.com/cdn/shop/t/263/assets/section-faqs.css?v=42096046378158829411693513939" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all">

    <div class="faqs container" style="--section-width: 100%;">

      <ul class="faqs__items accordion js-accordion" data-animation="on" data-multi-items="off" data-component="accordion">

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-0" id="accordion-header-6-0">
            <span>What Is Permanent Jewelry?</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--accordion-arrow accordion__icon-arrow no-js:is-hidden" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-0" id="accordion-content-6-0">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>Permanent jewelry is a type of jewelry that is crafted to be worn indefinitely. Unlike traditional jewelry, which may need to be taken off and cleaned or replaced, permanent jewelry is meant to be worn all the time. That said, by it’s nature it is still precious jewelry and needs to be given the care and attention to ensure it will last as long as possible (please don’t think you can play sports while wearing it!). It's an excellent option for people who want a piece of jewelry that is both stylish and practical. With permanent jewelry, you don't have to worry about moving parts like clasps.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-1" id="accordion-header-6-1">
            <span>Permanent Jewelry Supplies and Materials</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--accordion-arrow accordion__icon-arrow no-js:is-hidden" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-1" id="accordion-content-6-1">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>We use only the highest quality materials to create our permanent jewelry. Our materials include sterling silver and 14k gold. For a truly unique piece of jewelry you may want to learn more about how JewlVisiong can design you a <a href="https://www.marks-jewelers.com/pages/jewlvision?view=jewlvision"><span style="text-decoration:underline">custom piece of jewelry</span></a>. We also use a process to ensure that our jewelry is both as durable and safe as it can be for long-term wear.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-2" id="accordion-header-6-2">
            <span>How To Do Permanent Jewelry</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--accordion-arrow accordion__icon-arrow no-js:is-hidden" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>

          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-2" id="accordion-content-6-2">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>Getting a permanent piece of jewelry is a simple process that can be completed in just one visit to our store. Our experienced artisans will work with you to design a custom piece that reflects your style and personality. Browse our stunning<a href="https://www.marks-jewelers.com/pages/permanently-linked"><span style="text-decoration:underline"> collection of chains</span></a> to choose what style suits you best. Once the design is finalized, we'll use our state-of-the-art equipment to safely and effectively link the jewelry together permanently.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-3" id="accordion-header-6-3">
            <span>Link Permanent Jewelry</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--accordion-arrow accordion__icon-arrow no-js:is-hidden" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-3" id="accordion-content-6-3">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>Linking permanent jewelry involves creating a small opening in the skin and inserting a piece of jewelry directly underneath. Our team of professionals uses the latest techniques to ensure that the process is safe, sterile, and completely pain-free. The result is a beautiful piece of jewelry that becomes a part of you and lasts a lifetime.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-4" id="accordion-header-6-4">
            <span>How Much Is Permanent Jewelry?</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--accordion-arrow accordion__icon-arrow no-js:is-hidden" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-4" id="accordion-content-6-4">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>The cost of permanent jewelry depends on the type of jewelry and the materials used. Our experienced staff can work with you to design a custom piece that fits your budget. Sterling silver jewelry starts around $50 and gold jewelry at $105. The weight of the chain and length determine what your final cost will be. The saying “life happens” certainly applies to permanent bracelets and anklets. As there is no clasp, the chains need to be more delicate in nature. To properly protect your purchase, we recommend buying a warranty so that even if you lose your jewelry, we will replace it at no cost.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
          <button class="reset accordion__header js-accordion__trigger js-tab-focus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-content-6-5" id="accordion-header-6-5">
            <span>How To Clean Permanent Jewelry</span>
