              <g class="icon__group" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="3" y2="7"></line>
                <line x1="17" y1="7" x2="10" y2="14"></line>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel" aria-labelledby="accordion-header-6-5" id="accordion-content-6-5">
            <div class="accordion__panel-content">
              <p>Cleaning permanent jewelry is simple and easy. We recommend using a mild soap and warm water to gently clean the jewelry. Avoid using harsh chemicals or abrasive materials, as these can damage the jewelry over time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="accordion__item js-accordion__item ">
